---
title: Contact - HTHW
description: HTHW makes it easier to help people facing homelessness. Here's how to get in touch.
image: https://streetsupport.net/assets/img/og/street-support.jpg
layout: default.hbs
permalink: false
jsBundle: contact
section: about
page: contact
---

<div class="block block--breadcrumbs">
  <div class="container">
    <ol class="breadcrumbs__list">
      <li class="breadcrumbs__item"><a href="/">Home</a></li>
    <li class="breadcrumbs__item"><a href="/about">About</a></li>
      <li class="breadcrumbs__item">Contact</li>
    </ol>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="block block--header">
  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="h1 block__header">Contact Us</h1>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="block">
  <div class="container block__inner">
    <div class="block__content">
      <p class="text-center">
        <strong>Please note that we do not run any frontline services at the current moment. Please check for suitable organizations in the
          <a href="/find-help/">Find Help</a> section if you are experiencing homelessness and need support.</strong>
      </p>

      <div id="js-output" class="template"></div>

      <h2 class="h2">General enquiries</h2>
      <p>If you have any questions, ideas, or would like to know more about us, you can get in touch at
        <a href="mailto:hthcoin@gmail.com">hthcoin@gmail.com</a>.</p>

      <h2 class="h2">Locations</h2>
      <p>For questions specific to one of our locations, please contact our admins at the following address:</p>

      <ul>
        <li>
          <a href="mailto:leeds@streetsupport.net">support@hthcoin.world</a>
        </li>
       </ul>

      <h2 class="h2">Join the conversation</h2>
      <p>You can join the conversation on
        <a href="https://twitter.com/hthcoin">Twitter</a>,
        <a href="https://www.facebook.com/HelpTheHomelessCoinOfficial/">Facebook</a>.</p>
        </div>
  </div>
</div>


<script id="js-tpl" type="text/template">
  <div class="result-detail">
    <div class="accordion js-accordion">
    \{{#qAndAs}}
      <h3 class="h3 accordion__header js-header">
        \{{{question}}}
        <svg class="svg-plus-dims accordion__icon accordion__icon--open"><use xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" xlink:href="/assets/svgsprite.svg#plus"></use></svg>
        <svg class="svg-minus-dims accordion__icon accordion__icon--close"><use xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" xlink:href="/assets/svgsprite.svg#minus"></use></svg>
      </h3>
      <div class="accordion__item js-item">
        <div class="accordion__inner">
          <div class="result-detail__item">
            \{{{answer}}}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    \{{/qAndAs}}
    </div>
  </div>
</script>
